    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I asked about this in IRC when you first brought up this topic, but I didn't see a response: what is our existing mod-defined `ISpriteSequence` / `ISpriteSequenceLoader` code missing for your use case?\r\n\r\nThe sequence loaders can return `Sprite` subclasses that contain extra data, which is how we handle the per-image depth maps in the gen2 mods ([DefaultSpriteSequence.cs#L207](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/bleed/OpenRA.Mods.Common/Graphics/DefaultSpriteSequence.cs#L207)).  This PR appears to be duplicating that feature at the SheetBuilder level?"
  },
