    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "While it doesn't affect this PR directly, I have a strong caution about how I assume you are using this in your mod code:  You said in IRC that you want to use this for positioning turrets on actors.  Turret positions are important for the simulation state (since it controls where projectiles are fired from), but Sprite objects are only available from the rendering code.  Rendering is decoupled from simulation, and the game will desync in multiplayer if you try to modify simulation state from render code."
  },
